column1: Daily Weather Observations for Gunnedah, New South Wales for September 2021
Prepared at 13:00 UTC on Thursday 21 October 2021   IDCJDW2056.202109
Most observations from Gunnedah Airport, but some from Gunnedah Soil Conservation Service.
Temperature, humidity, wind, pressure and rainfall observations are from Gunnedah Airport AWS {station 055202}
Cloud and evaporation observations are from Gunnedah Resource Centre {station 055024}
